    num = int(input())

card = list(x for x in range(1, num + 1))

while len(card) != 1:
    del card[0]
    temp = card[0]
    for i in range(1, len(card)):
        card[i - 1] = card[i]
    card[len(card)-1] = temp

print(card[0])

    from collections import deque

n = int(input())

a = [i for i in range(1, n + 1)]
a = deque(a)

while len(a) != 1:

    a.popleft()
    num = a.popleft()

    a.append(num)

print(a[0])
